1
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:10,960
Have something to eat.

2
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:14,170
Come to the cooperative when you feel better.

3
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:48,960
You're awake.

4
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:49,920
How are you feeling?

5
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,520
Does your head hurt? Are you uncomfortable?

6
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,680
Does your stomach burn?

7
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,200
Did you eat the plain congee?

8
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,000
You...

9
00:01:55,479 --> 00:01:56,920
You're asking so many questions.

10
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,720
Which one should I answer first?

11
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,200
Wait a minute.

12
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,320
Look.

13
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:09,199
Our logistics subsidy application has been approved.

14
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,000
Also,

15
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:11,760
Early this morning, Li Cong brought the contract

16
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:13,000
to the village committee

17
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,760
and signed a one-year contract with me.

18
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,560
Really?

19
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:18,280
It's 10% less than the agreed price at that time.

20
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,480
He asked me to tell you

21
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:22,880
