22
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:23,720
That's great.

23
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:26,079
I just passed by the goji berry orchard.

24
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,410
The berries are red.

25
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,640
I also discussed it with Aunt Guli and the others.

26
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,640
We can start picking them tomorrow.

27
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,320
Recently, many netizens

28
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,560
have messaged me asking about the broadcast time.

29
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,440
It should be ready.

30
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,600
Why don't

31
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,880
you come in and check it out with me?

32
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:42,680
Let's go.

33
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,360
After the logistics issues,

34
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,020
everyone blamed themselves.

35
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:02,480
They felt worse about those fresh goji berries than anyone else.

36
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,880
They came to us on their own initiative,

37
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:06,760
saying they wanted to learn professional packing techniques.

38
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,090
Farming during the day,

39
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,760
they gathered at night

40
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:11,160
to learn from videos.

41
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,840
When they encountered something they didn't understand,

42
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,480
they immediately contacted experts

43
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,680
for online guidance.

44
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:16,960
Secretary.

45
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,960
Look, in just one minute now,

46
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,720
I can pack two parcels.

47
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,840
I pack a bit slower,

48
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,720
but,

49
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,640
I pack the best. Look.

50
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:30,130
Sister Ren Zhen.

51
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,320
I swear on the calluses on my hands,

52
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:35,160
there will be absolutely no problem this time.

53
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,720
Rest assured.

54
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:39,160
The quality will definitely pass.

55
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,040
Then,

56
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,800
let's start the livestream.

57
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,920
Okay.

58
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:53,600
I'll take it.

59
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,770
Here, Aunt Guli.

60
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:58,570
Pack fresh ones.

61
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,560
Okay.

62
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,560
These fruits are really good.

63
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,290
Grandpa Bate, look at this one.

64
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,520
Follow us for a chance to win prizes.

65
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,520
Grand prizes, coupons, and fine gifts

66
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,520
are all up for grabs.

67
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,440
Just place an order in my live stream,

68
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:13,520
and you'll get a chance for the lucky draw.

69
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,320
Friends,

70
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:16,560
I am your good friend Wulan.

71
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:20,079
I am a good friend of your Goji Berry Prince.

72
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:23,160
We are tentatively scheduled for next Friday

73
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,490
to start the broadcast.

74
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:30,040
In the livestream, it's not 59.9,

75
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,520
not 49.9.

76
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:34,680
Just a surprise price of 29.9.

77
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:37,520
Remember next Friday,

78
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:39,720
at the same time. The broadcast begins.

79
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,840
Three, two, one.

80
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,800
We're live.

81
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:47,280
Welcome to the Xiacun agricultural support live stream.

82
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,600
First, I'd like to introduce

83
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,880
our goji berries.

84
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,280
This is the improved packaging.

85
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:57,480
Jiangda Express is really reliable.

86
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,640
The tracking shows that parcels sent out the day before

87
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,240
reach the customers the very next day.

88
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,280
And the online store's backend

89
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,920
is full of positive reviews.

90
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:06,160
What about our return rate?

91
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,760
You mean

92
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:10,000
the customers who ordered during our first stream?

93
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,720
Yes.

94
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:13,200
That's called the repurchase rate.

95
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,040
It's around 30%.

96
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,960
But don't worry.

97
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:18,760
Give it some time and space, and it will get better.

98
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,290
Secretary Jiao.

99
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,880
Village Head Tie.

100
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:22,810
Long time no see.

101
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,290
Branch Secretary Chen.

102
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,360
Mayor Ha.

103
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,440
Secretary Abudu.

104
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,040
Why are you all here?

105
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:30,640
Please help us. Please help us.

106
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,570
Secretary Jiao.

107
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,760
She must be the treasure of our Xia Village.

108
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,560
Yes.

109
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,480
Let me introduce you.

110
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,159
This is the person in charge

111
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:48,680
of the e-commerce business in our Xia Village.

112
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,480
She is capable and experienced.

113
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,080
Hello, everyone. My name is Ren Zhen.

114
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,400
I heard from the young people in our village

115
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:59,560
that Xia Village's e-commerce livestreaming

116
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,760
is doing really well,

117
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,440
and their goji berries are selling great.

118
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:04,640
But as for the internet,

119
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,240
we know absolutely nothing.

120
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,680
I heard that a single internet cable

121
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,760
can change a village's destiny.

122
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:13,600
Come, try our village's crabapples.

123
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,720
They were just picked from the trees this morning.

124
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,920
Please, have a taste.

125
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:19,180
Try some. They're delicious.

126
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,920
Very sweet and crisp.

127
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:25,560
And they're much bigger

128
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,400
than the ones I usually see.

129
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,960
These are Xiangfei crabapples.

130
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,960
Their skin is covered with

131
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,280
a thin layer of bloom.

132
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,640
Their sweetness level is over 20.

133
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,760
Thin skin and very juicy.

134
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,040
Sweet and sour.

135
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,520
They are the best of the best.

136
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,960
Come, try our red grapes.

137
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,520
Secretary Abudu,

138
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:47,320
this must be our star product.

139
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,400
Yes.

140
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,360
Try some.

141
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,840
I've loved eating these since I was a kid.

142
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:53,520
Bole red grapes.

143
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,440
Their skin

144
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:56,500
is so thin it's almost non-existent.

145
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,320
They taste sweet and fragrant.

146
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,720
After eating, the fruity aroma lingers in your mouth.

147
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,650
Secretary Chen,

148
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:04,370
your village is at 45 degrees north latitude,

149
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,120
the golden corn belt.

150
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:08,240
The corn grown there must be delicious.

151
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:10,240
Secretary Jiao, you're absolutely right.

152
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:12,440
Our corn is the best.

153
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,960
This corn is soft and waxy.

154
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,600
And it has high nutritional value.

155
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,920
Many of my friends from out of town

156
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,560
ask me to send them more.

157
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,800
When you go back this time,

158
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,240
make sure to take some more.

159
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:23,880
Okay.

160
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,040
Mayor Ha.

161
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,720
These yogurt bumps

162
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:30,160
are our local specialty.

163
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,680
When I am away,

164
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,040
sometimes for research

165
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,200
or business trips,

166
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:36,120
I keep them in my briefcase.

167
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,240
Every time I chew them,

168
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:39,440
they taste better and better.

169
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,920
You don't feel homesick after eating them, right?

170
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,560
Right.

171
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,360
Definitely.

172
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,360
And yak meat,

173
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,320
rye flour.

174
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:47,840
These are all good things from Bozhou.

175
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,600
The reason why I know so much

176
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,400
is because

177
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:52,159
a teacher named Yin Changying

178
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:53,640
inspired me a lot.

179
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:54,880
She let me know

180
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,560
that Bozhou has many local specialties

181
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,090
worth promoting out there.

182
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,000
Actually, even if you hadn't come today,

183
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,320
I would have wanted to visit your village.

184
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,120
A few days ago,

185
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:05,440
I recommended mulberry leaf tea to netizens.

186
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:07,720
As long as there is a chance for people to know,

187
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,650
good things will naturally shine.

188
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,480
Right?

189
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,400
Yes, yes, yes.

190
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,280
As village cadres,

191
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:15,280
we should take the lead in promoting

192
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:16,360
all the good things of Bozhou,

193
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,800
so that every effort on this land

194
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,920
can be rewarded.

195
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,040
Secretary Jiao,

196
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,680
you are an outstanding youth

197
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,840
of Bortala.

198
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,480
I seem to

199
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:30,560
understand the meaning of your return to the village.

200
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,400
Thank you for understanding me.

201
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,640
Ren Zhen,

202
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,919
why are you here?

203
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:01,010
Do you have Village Head Tie's contact information?

204
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,200
Mr. Xiao Chu,

205
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,680
I have already resigned.

206
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,280
Please don't call me again.

207
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,200
Ren Zhen,

208
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,280
I'm calling to tell you

209
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,810
that I've left Shangle.

210
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:25,440
I'm really sorry for how I treated you in the past for the sake of the company's performance.

211
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,200
Your hard work and capability are obvious to all.

212
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,200
Are you interested in starting a business with me?

213
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,720
I'll give you the position of COO.

214
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,520
Well...

215
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,980
No rush. Take your time to think about it.

216
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,960
I see your IP address has been in Xinjiang.

217
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,290
Aren't you coming back?

218
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,640
Come back.
